# VoiceCrack – Audio Visualisation Engines

> Located in `js/engines/`  
> Both engines are pure Canvas renderers with no DOM dependencies beyond their canvas element.  
> They are fully decoupled from each other and from the audio pipeline — they only consume processed data.

---

## Architecture Principle

```
Audio Pipeline (studio.js)
    │
    ├─ levelEngine.frame(rms)          ← raw RMS amplitude, every frame
    └─ pitchTrailEngine.frame(midi)    ← median-filtered MIDI note, every frame
```

Engines are instantiated once per `render()` call and reset on recording start.  
They are destroyed implicitly when the page navigates away (canvas detached from DOM).

---

## LevelEngine

**File:** `js/engines/levelEngine.js`  
**Purpose:** Horizontal RMS amplitude bar with peak-hold marker and Vocal Luminescence gradient fill.

### Constructor

```js
const engine = new LevelEngine(canvasElement, options?);
```

| Option | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `peakDecayRate` | `0.006` | Peak hold decay per frame (0 = no decay, 1 = instant) |
| `emaAlpha` | `0.20` | EMA smoothing factor for bar fill (faster than trail) |

### Methods

| Method | Description |
|---|---|
| `frame(rms)` | Feed one RMS value. Call every animation frame. |
| `reset()` | Clears bar and peak. Call on recording start. |

### Visual Anatomy

```
[━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━|         ]
 ← gradient fill (rms level) ──────────→  ^peak     ^empty
```

- **Fill gradient:** `#6b3fa0` (deep violet) → `#b6a0ff` (primary) → `#00f1fe` (cyan at 100%)
- **Peak marker:** 2px white bar that holds for ~0.5 s then decays at `peakDecayRate`
- **Canvas:** 8px tall pill (`border-radius: 999px` via container), full width
- **DPR-aware:** resizes with `devicePixelRatio` for crisp rendering on Retina displays

### Tuning Parameters

| Parameter | Value | Effect if increased | Effect if decreased |
|---|---|---|---|
| `emaAlpha` | `0.20` | Bar reacts faster, jumpier | Bar moves sluggishly |
| `peakDecayRate` | `0.006` | Peak drops faster | Peak holds longer |

