## Future: Arena Challenge Integration

The `PitchTrailEngine` is challenge-ready. The Arena page will:

1. Define a challenge sequence (array of `{ midi, durationMs }` target notes)
2. Call `trail.setTarget(midi)` as each note becomes active
3. Poll `trail.getAccuracy()` to score the user
4. Advance to the next note when hold time is met

```js
// Pseudocode — Arena challenge runner
for (const note of challengeNotes) {
    trail.setTarget(note.midi);
    await holdFor(note.durationMs, () => trail.getAccuracy().isHit);
    score += trail.getAccuracy().isHit ? 1 : 0;
}
trail.setTarget(null);
```
